4.11	Pedro_Mir	Pedro Mir	Pedro Julio Mir Valentín (3 June 1913, San Pedro de Macorís – 11 July 2000, Santo Domingo) was a Dominican poet and writer, named Poet Laureate of the Dominican Republic by Congress in 1984, and a member of the generation of "Independent poets of the 1940s" in Dominican poetry.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/42/Pedro_mir.jpg
